stimulus:

responses: {"Q0":"Jason has stage 2 lymphoma and because our stupid American healthcare system is for-profit, he can't afford his chemotherapy. We need Medicare for all. Until we get it, we need to crowdfund to help people like Jason stay alive."}

{"Q0":"I think you're testing to see how much people are willing to donate to a crowdfunded medical treatment. In this case--I don't know Jason, and he's in Stage 2. I sometimes don't give any money to people I don't know because it could be a scam. I have donated all of the money I made here at Mechanical Turk in the last year because I wanted Medicare for All to pass. I donated almost $2000 to Bernie Sanders' campaign.
